  "keyFeatures": [
    "Vial-compatible keyboard auto-detection and connection via Raw HID",
    "Real-time keymap editor with drag-and-drop layer management",
    "Multi-type macro system (infrared, combo keys, text input, app launch, AI text conversion)",
    "Visual workflow automation builder with time and event-based triggers",
    "Cloud-synced infrared remote control codes via Firebase Firestore",
    "AI-powered text transformation using Gemini AI (summarization, tone conversion, etc.)",
    "Windows system tray integration with background key monitoring",
    "Modern UI with Rive animations and glassmorphism design"
  ],
